    "title": {
        "rendered": "YouTube embed"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right has-small-font-size\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/blocks/\">Go back to the list of <strong>Blocks</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-8.52.08-AM.png\" alt=\"YouTube icon\" class=\"wp-image-12707620\" style=\"width:61px;height:49px\" width=\"61\" height=\"49\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the YouTube Embed block you can include a YouTube video into your post/page with play buttons, so your visitor can stay on your site to watch it. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You don&#8217;t need a YouTube account to embed a video.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not all videos can be shared this way, though. The publisher needs to &#8220;Allow Embedding&#8221; in the settings of the video and some publishers restrict the countries, where videos can be shared. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"261\" height=\"85\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-8.54.45-AM.png\" alt=\"This setting can be found YouTube Studio:\nEdit Video &gt; More Options &gt; Check &quot;Allow embedding\" class=\"wp-image-12707638\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">This setting can be found YouTube Studio:  <br>Edit Video &gt; More Options &gt; Check &#8220;Allow embedding</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Non-personal identifying viewing data will be shared with YouTube and the publisher of the video. <em>Please consult the <a href=\"https://support.google.com/policies/answer/9664901\">privacy policies and information</a> on YouTube if your site is visited by children.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Six Steps to embed a YouTube Video in your post or page</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Find your video on YouTube.com, and copy the URL of the video from the browser bar</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/YouTube-Embed-URL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12707768\" style=\"width:458px;height:344px\" width=\"458\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/YouTube-Embed-URL.jpg 960w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/YouTube-Embed-URL-300x225.jpg 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/YouTube-Embed-URL-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Add a YouTube Embed block to your post. </strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-wordpress-5-9.png\" alt=\"Select a YouTube block for Gutenberg Page Builder\" class=\"wp-image-15327736\" style=\"width:350px;height:501px\" width=\"350\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-wordpress-5-9.png 631w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-wordpress-5-9-209x300.png 209w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding a block via the &#8220;Slash&#8221; command from an empty row</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/adding-a-new-block/\">Detailed instructions on adding blocks</a></p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Paste the YouTube URL </strong>from Step 1</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Click on the &#8220;Embed&#8221; Button</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"411\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-1024x411.png\" alt=\"YouTube URL paste example into block\" class=\"wp-image-15327745\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-1024x411.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-300x121.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-768x309.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9.png 1170w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"5\">\n<li><strong>You see the YouTube video in your editor.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-post-embed-1024x830.png\" alt=\"Example of video being added in block - WordPress 5.9\" class=\"wp-image-15327751\" style=\"width:360px;height:292px\" width=\"360\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-post-embed-1024x830.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-post-embed-300x243.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-post-embed-768x622.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-post-embed.png 1170w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">After Embed of a YouTube video</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"6\">\n<li><strong>Clicking on Preview</strong>, will show you the display on the front end of your page. </li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"878\" height=\"517\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-9.32.38-AM.png\" alt=\"YouTube Video Block - Embed Success\" class=\"wp-image-12707920\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-9.32.38-AM.png 878w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-9.32.38-AM-300x177.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-9.32.38-AM-768x452.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 878px) 100vw, 878px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\">Embed other YouTube links</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Playlist</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A playlist URL can be embedded and the first video of the list shows in the embed box, with additional navigation for the playlist in the top right corner. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-playlist-example-5-9-1-1024x812.png\" alt=\"Playlist example of YouTube Gutenberg Block\" class=\"wp-image-15327770\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Live Streams</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>YouTube Live stream URLs are supported in the form of <code>youtube.com/live/videocode</code></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Unsupported URLs</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Not all YouTube links can be used for an embed. When an URL is used that is not suited for embedding, the Block editor offers you two options: to try a different URL or convert the current URL into a Text link. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-video-not-found-1024x683.png\" alt=\"Sorry - Content cannot be embedded example from Youtube.\" class=\"wp-image-15327779\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-video-not-found-1024x683.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-video-not-found-300x200.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-video-not-found-768x512.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-video-not-found.png 1214w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"block-toolbar\">Block Toolbar</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Next to the YouTube icon is the &#8220;Drag &amp; Drop Handle&#8221;. This can be used to drag your block to another section of your page. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next to this is the &#8220;Mover&#8221;. Up and Down options are presented.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-5-9.png\" alt=\"Block toolbar for the YouTube block\" class=\"wp-image-15327817\" style=\"width:358px;height:68px\" width=\"358\" height=\"68\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-5-9.png 465w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-5-9-300x57.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">YouTube block toolbar</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Change Alignment</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>After the first separator line you have the &#8220;Change alignment&#8221; tool. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-alignment.png\" alt=\"Changing alignment for the YouTube block\" class=\"wp-image-15327845\" style=\"width:349px;height:321px\" width=\"349\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-alignment.png 600w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-toolbar-alignment-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Change alignment option &#8211; YouTube Block</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The alignment has variable options depending on your theme. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>None </strong>&#8211; Default alignment option.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>Wide width </strong>&#8211; Increase the width of the post beyond the content size.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>Full width</strong> &#8211; Extend the block to cover the full width of the screen.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>Align left</strong> &#8211; Make the block left-aligned.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>Align center </strong>&#8211; Make the block alignment centered.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><strong><strong><strong>Align right </strong>&#8211; Make the block right aligned.</strong></strong></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cWide width\u201d and \u201cFull width\u201d alignment need to be enabled by the Theme of your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Edit URL</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on the Edit button will bring up the view for adjusting your URL for the Video Embed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"411\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-1024x411.png\" alt=\"YouTube URL paste example into block\" class=\"wp-image-15327745\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-1024x411.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-300x121.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9-768x309.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/02/youtube-block-add-url-5-9.png 1170w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Via the edit URL, you can change the YouTube Embed URL in the embed block. Overwrite the existing URL and click on the &#8220;Embed&#8221; button on the right.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>More Options</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>These controls give you the option to copy, duplicate, and edit your block as HTML.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-background\" style=\"background-color:#e5f5fa\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/more-options/\">Read about these and other settings.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"block-settings\">Block Settings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides the &#8220;Advanced&#8221; section, the YouTube embed has only one setting in the \u201cBlock Settings\u201d sidebar: Media Settings. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\">Media Settings</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-9 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"406\" height=\"182\" data-id=\"12701737\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.46-AM.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12701737\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.46-AM.png 406w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.46-AM-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 406px) 100vw, 406px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"408\" height=\"197\" data-id=\"12701738\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.55-AM.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12701738\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.55-AM.png 408w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-20-at-9.29.55-AM-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 408px) 100vw, 408px\" /></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Via the <em>Media Settings</em> you can control the behavior of your post embed when viewed from a smaller device, like on a  phone screen. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Toggle switch turns on or off the resize functionality for smaller devices. The default setting is &#8220;on&#8221; or blue. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&#8220;Off:&#8221;</strong> This embed may not preserve its aspect ratio when the browser is resized. In the off position the toggle switch is gray. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&#8220;On:&#8221;</strong> This embed will preserve its aspect ratio when the browser is resized. The toggle switch turns blue in the &#8220;On&#8221; position. </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Advanced</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The advanced tab lets you add a CSS class to your block, allowing you to write custom CSS and style the block as you see fit.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-10.06.40-AM.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"418\" height=\"226\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-10.06.40-AM.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12708156\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-10.06.40-AM.png 418w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-21-at-10.06.40-AM-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 418px) 100vw, 418px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The advanced section lets you add a CSS class to your block.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For a YouTube embed there are default CSS classes to allow for responsive handling of the embed when viewed on smaller devices like mobile phones. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group changelog has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\" id=\"changelog\">Changelog</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Updated 2023-08-24\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Added Live Streams section</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2022-11-23\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Removed redundant data</li>\n\n\n\n<li>added alt text on some images </li>\n\n\n\n<li>aligned images for mobile view </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2022-02-04\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Change Screenshots to 5.9</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Removed the group area from toolbar options</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated the flow of the document to represent what is in the toolbar</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated labels for more settings to fit 5.9</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2020-08-18\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Replaced \u201cMore Options\u201d \u2013 new screenshot</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added \u201cMove To\u201d and \u201cCopy\u201d section under More Options</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updated 2020-05-26\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Fixed some typos</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Created 2020-04-21</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
